title: S15 Ep50: The Haunting of the Cabin on Route 360
itunes:title: The Haunting of the Cabin on Route 360
description:
Darkness Radio enter The Haunting of the Cabin on Rte 360 with guests Ryan & Ryanna Jones and Dennis Estlock!

There is a mysterious plot of land, soaked in the blood of history and tragedy. Today Dave and Tim enter this story to reveal its dark histories and hauntings, to confront terror and manipulation in alarming ways. So sit back, turn down the lights, pull the blankets up over your head and get ready for an epic ParaShare!

Visit their page here: https://www.facebook.com/Haunted360houses/
